description: The physician referral data linked below was provided as a response to a Freedom of Information Act (FOIA) request. These files represent the number of encounters a single beneficiary has had across physicians at intervals of 30, 60, 90 and 180 days. For more details about the file contents for years 2009 - 2015, please see the Technical Requirements document.

title: Physician Shared Patient Patterns
